txt.en: Follow Khâshap to the Gate of Storms
Chase Khâshap to the Gate of Sorrow!
Khâshap has lured you into the Gut, and has turned the streets against you. Give chase as he makes his way to his master!

From the apothecaries of Carn Dûm to Langstrand all the way to Umbar, Indagir now known as Khâshap has been transporting a draught of the vilest make. We now grasp at his heels as he makes his final attempt to deliver this substance to his master. We will not fail. We cannot. Khâshap must be stopped, now!
Khâshap and the Bile of Ifrinn are no more
Khâshap has left you to deal with his most trusted cohort, Utho the Grasper.\n\nDefeat Utho the Grasper.
Khâshap has taken to the Fleetfast. He is running out of places to run. You must corner him at last!
Khâshap has fled deeper into the back streets. Continue your pursuit before he delivers the Bile of Ifrinn!
Khâshap has been cornered at the Gate of Storms. You must defeat him before he can make his final attempt at delivering this Bile of Ifrinn to his master.
The Streets of Râhal Bakh -- Tier 1
